4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for individuals without prior experience, aiming to facilitate a swift transition into a cybersecurity career. The program spans 16 weeks and includes 3 live online classes per week, capped at 16 participants per class. It covers essential areas such as Windows and Linux systems, networking, cloud security, penetration testing, and compliance with standards like ISO 27001. Students will earn an Official 4Geeks Completion Certificate, widely recognized in the industry. The coursework is available in both English and Spanish. For more information, visit: https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity. stop